<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Papi Trader — Jose Miguel Escobar</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700;900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold: #D4AF37;
            --gold-light: #F5E6A3;
            --dark: #0A0A0A;
            --dark-card: #111111;
            --dark-surface: #1A1A1A;
            --text: #E8E8E8;
            --text-muted: #888888;
            --accent-green: #00C853;
            --accent-red: #FF1744;
            --gradient-gold: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4AF37 0%, #F5E6A3 50%, #D4AF37 100%);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: var(--text);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ===== PRELOADER ===== */
        .preloader {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 10000;
            transition: opacity 0.8s ease, visibility 0.8s ease;
        }

        .preloader.hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
        }

        .preloader-content {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .preloader-logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .preloader-bar {
            width: 200px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--dark-surface);
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .preloader-bar::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 40%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            animation: loading 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes loading {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(350%); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }

        /* ===== NAVIGATION ===== */
        .nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }

        .nav.scrolled {
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            padding: 15px 60px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-brand {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--gold);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* ===== HERO SECTION ===== */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('images/papi-hero.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
            filter: brightness(0.3);
            transform: scale(1.1);
            animation: heroZoom 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes heroZoom {
            0% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1.0); }
        }

        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(
                to bottom,
                rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.4) 0%,
                rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.2) 50%,
                rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9) 100%
            );
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 0 80px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .hero-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.3s both;
        }

        .hero-name {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 5rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.5s both;
        }

        .hero-name span {
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.7s both;
        }

        .hero-quote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.9s both;
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 50px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 1.1s both;
        }

        .hero-stat {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .hero-stat-value {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 1.5s both;
        }

        .scroll-indicator span {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .scroll-line {
            width: 1px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--gold);
            animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes scrollPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scaleY(0.5); }
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* ===== SECTIONS COMMON ===== */
        .section {
            padding: 120px 80px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .section-title span {
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 60px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* ===== ABOUT SECTION ===== */
        .about {
            background: var(--dark);
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-image {
            position: relative;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 4px;
            filter: grayscale(20%);
            transition: filter 0.5s ease;
        }

        .about-image:hover img {
            filter: grayscale(0%);
        }

        .about-image-border {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 4px;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .about-text p:first-letter {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        /* ===== TIMELINE ===== */
        .timeline-section {
            background: var(--dark-card);
        }

        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 1px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
        }

        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) {
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .timeline-content {
            width: 45%;
            padding: 30px;
            background: var(--dark-surface);
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .timeline-content:hover {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .timeline-dot {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid var(--dark);
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .timeline-year {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .timeline-desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* ===== PHILOSOPHY ===== */
        .philosophy {
            background: var(--dark);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .philosophy-quote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: var(--gold-light);
        }

        .philosophy-author {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .philosophy-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 80px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .phil-card {
            padding: 40px;
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .phil-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease;
        }

        .phil-card:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .phil-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }

        .phil-card-number {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .phil-card-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .phil-card-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* ===== LIFESTYLE ===== */
        .lifestyle {
            background: var(--dark-card);
        }

        .lifestyle-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            height: 600px;
        }

        .lifestyle-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .lifestyle-item:first-child {
            grid-row: 1 / 3;
        }

        .lifestyle-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
        }

        .lifestyle-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .lifestyle-item-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.8));
        }

        .lifestyle-item-text {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* ===== PROFILE FACTS ===== */
        .facts {
            background: var(--dark);
        }

        .facts-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .fact-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 25px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .fact-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .fact-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text);
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* ===== CTA SECTION ===== */
        .cta-section {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 80px;
        }

        .cta-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-title span {
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .cta-sub {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 16px 40px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-gold {
            background: var(--gradient-gold);
            color: var(--dark);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .btn-gold:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--gold);
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: var(--gold);
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
        .footer {
            padding: 40px 80px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav { padding: 15px 20px; }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
            .hero-content { padding: 0 20px; }
            .hero-name { font-size: 2.8rem; }
            .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
            .section { padding: 60px 20px; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
            .philosophy-quote { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .philosophy-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .lifestyle-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; height: auto; }
            .lifestyle-item:first-child { grid-row: auto; }
            .lifestyle-item { height: 300px; }
            .facts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .timeline::before { left: 20px; }
            .timeline-item, .timeline-item:nth-child(even) { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; padding-left: 50px; }
            .timeline-content { width: 100%; }
            .timeline-dot { left: 20px; }
            .cta-section { padding: 60px 20px; }
            .footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; text-align: center; }
        }

        /* ===== SCROLL ANIMATIONS ===== */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(50px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease;
        }

        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- PRELOADER -->
    <div class="preloader" id="preloader">
        <div class="preloader-content">
            <div class="preloader-logo">PAPI TRADER</div>
            <div class="preloader-bar"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- NAVIGATION -->
    <nav class="nav" id="nav">
        <a href="#" class="nav-brand">Papi Trader</a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#about">Обо мне</a></li>
            <li><a href="#journey">Мой путь</a></li>
            <li><a href="#philosophy">Философия</a></li>
            <li><a href="#lifestyle">Стиль жизни</a></li>
            <li><a href="#profile">Профиль</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Контакт</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-tag">Trader · Educator · Content Creator</div>
            <h1 class="hero-name">Jose Miguel<br><span>Escobar</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Papi Trader — Miami, FL</p>
            <p class="hero-quote">«Деньги — это не цель. Это инструмент свободы, который ты даёшь себе сам.»</p>
            <div class="hero-stats">
                <div class="hero-stat">
                    <div class="hero-stat-value">9+</div>
                    <div class="hero-stat-label">Лет в трейдинге</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stat">
                    <div class="hero-stat-value">50K+</div>
                    <div class="hero-stat-label">Студентов онлайн</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stat">
                    <div class="hero-stat-value">12</div>
                    <div class="hero-stat-label">Стран аудитории</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator">
            <span>Scroll</span>
            <div class="scroll-line"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ABOUT -->
    <section class="section about" id="about">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-image reveal">
                <img src="images/papi-phone.jpg" alt="Papi Trader">
                <div class="about-image-border"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-text reveal">
                <div class="section-label">Обо мне</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Меня зовут <span>Хосе Мигель</span></h2>
                <div class="divider"></div>
                <p>Я родился в Мехико, в обычной семье — отец работал на фабрике, мать вела бухгалтерию для маленькой лавки. В 15 лет я написал свою первую программу на Pascal — и понял, что технологии могут вытащить меня из того мира, в котором я рос.</p>
                <p>В 18 я переехал в Гвадалахару, поступил на IT-факультет. Именно там, на втором курсе, один друг показал мне график биткоина. Это был 2015 год. Я потерял первые $200 за два дня. Но я не остановился — я влюбился в рынок.</p>
                <p>Сегодня я живу в Майами, управляю медиабрендом «Papi Trader», создаю обучающий контент на испанском и английском, и строю сообщество для молодых ребят из Латинской Америки, которые хотят изменить свою жизнь через финансовую грамотность.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TIMELINE -->
    <section class="section timeline-section" id="journey">
        <div class="section-label reveal" style="text-align:center;">Мой путь</div>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal" style="text-align:center;">От Мехико до <span>Майами</span></h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item reveal">
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2015</div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Первый контакт с рынком</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Открыл первый демо-счёт в 19 лет. Потерял $200 реальных денег за два дня — и решил, что должен разобраться по-настоящему. Читал всё: от японских свечей до психологии рынка.</div>
                </div>
